  contradictoryClaimId: CL001
  explanationText: "Greta claims she heard music from 4B at 10 PM. But the smart
    speaker log shows audio stopped at 8:42 PM and the wifi log shows the resident's
    phone disconnected from home at 8:55 PM. The speaker was silent at 10 PM \u2014
    Greta's testimony is impossible."
